{% extends "layout_project.njk" %}
{% block content %}
    {% from "_components.njk" import iframeVideo %}
    <div class = "text-center">
        <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase">Music-syncing Gramophone</h2>
        <p class="item-intro text-muted">Grade 12 Computer Engineering Team Project</p>
    </div>
    <!-- https://www.w3schools.com/bootstrap/bootstrap_carousel.asp
                    https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.0/components/carousel/ -->
    <div id="carouselGramophone" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <!-- Indicators -->
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#carouselGramophone" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselGramophone" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselGramophone" data-slide-to="2"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselGramophone" data-slide-to="3"></li>
        </ol>
        <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="../img/portfolio/gramophone/LPFA_schematic.jpg"
                        alt="Schematic of low pass filter" style="height:80vh">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <p>Original Design for the LPFA</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="../img/portfolio/gramophone/LPFA_traces.png" alt="circuit traces"
                        style="height:80vh">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <p>Circuit traces of the LPFA board</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="../img/portfolio/gramophone/Hinge1.gif" alt="GIF of STL file"
                        style="height:80vh">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <p>Hinge - part 1</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="../img/portfolio/gramophone/Hinge2.gif" alt="Gif of STL file"
                        style="height:80vh">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <p>Hinge - part 2</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Left and right controls -->
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselGramophone" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselGramophone" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="portfolio-description">
        <p>
                    Using the RAINBO board, my team and I designed a circuit to sync the flashing of multiple LED
                    strips to the bass channel of any song. We designed a Low-pass filter and amplifier circuit (dubbed
                    "LPFA") using circuits.io (now deprecated). The RAINBO board accepts an analog value (output from
                    LPFA board), adds it to the most recent ones. The top 4 values of the 10 most recent ones are
                    averaged, and the output is the number of LEDs that are lit up.
                  </p>
        <p>
                    During this project, I also created 3D printable hinges, as we were originally planning on having
                    petals open and close at the top of the gramophone.
                  </p>
        {{ iframeVideo("IfRoX2KtbN0") }}
        <p>Above is a demo video of the gramophone display, flashing in sync with the song "Ed Sheeran -
                    Shape of You".</p>
        {{ iframeVideo("DEA2j4OvXGA") }}
        <p>Above is a demo of the same, in the daytime.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center">
        <ul class="list-inline">
            <li>
                <a href="https://github.com/AbhinavA10/Gramophone-LPF" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Github Repo</a>
            </li>
            <li>Timeframe: Grade 12</li>
            <li>Relevant Technologies: C, Low-pass filters</li>
        </ul>
        <a  href="../projects.html">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button">
                <i class="fa fa-times"></i>
                  Close Project
            </button>
        </a>
    </div>
{% endblock %}